data.description: Unique property in an excellent neighborhood ideal for a large family or an investor. Includes: 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1,869 square feet and the lot is over 8,270 square feet. 1 huge bedroom with a walk-in closet. Laundry access on one side of the house added as a legal addition that could be a studio or 2 good sized rooms. Large yard surrounded by block walls. Home upgraded with a tile roof. Fruit trees, Long driveway for possible RV access. Central A/C and heating. Oversized covered patio. Tile flooring throughout the property, except the bedrooms, they have laminated flooring. Close to schools, parks and shopping. Front door faces EAST/WEST.
